<h1>Time for your SEAS Self Evaluation!</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name.presence || @user.email %>,</p>

<p>It's time to reflect on your growth! Your SEAS Self Evaluation is ready for you to complete. This evaluation covers four areas:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Social</strong> - How you interact and engage with others</li>
  <li><strong>Emotional</strong> - How you manage and express your emotions</li>
  <li><strong>Academic</strong> - How you approach learning and school</li>
  <li><strong>Spiritual</strong> - How you reflect on values and make positive choices</li>
</ul>

<p>Click the link below to get started:</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Start My SEAS Evaluation", @seas_url %>
</p>

<p>This link will expire in 30 days.</p>

<p>
  Thanks,<br>
  The High Aspirations Team
</p>
